    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/2e49f6ba3338e77e15939059a80b00c6.avif?t=1764731549\" width=616 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《义体伞兵：第一次下降》中，你将体验到无与伦比的道具搭配自由度！在试玩版中我们为您提供超过50种独特功能的义肢，每一个都能为你带来新的战斗策略与惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想让子弹分裂后爆炸？或者用跟踪子弹加上穿透效果？这些自由组合让每一场战斗都充满未知和爽快感！不断试验、组合，发现最适合你的战斗方式，让每一次挑战都带来1 + 1 &gt; 2的超爽战斗体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/ca13fb529011cb6bd9b9066fd30b10b6.poster.avif?t=1764731549\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/ca13fb529011cb6bd9b9066fd30b10b6.webm?t=1764731549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/ca13fb529011cb6bd9b9066fd30b10b6.mp4?t=1764731549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/04d350bcea937c75c1c999cc8c4ce057.avif?t=1764731549\" width=616 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《义体伞兵：第一次下降》融合了复古像素艺术与未来科技，每一层、每一个房间都充满了探索的惊喜！从空间站的避难所醒来，你将面临各种形态怪异的敌人和不明的危机。随着你深入，每一扇门背后隐藏的秘密都会带你接近真相。在这里，选择正确的方向，战斗每一个敌人，甚至能让你获得意想不到的强力道具。每一场战斗，都会让你感受到前所未有的爽快与挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/006142025b781db4313c79b496c64020.poster.avif?t=1764731549\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/006142025b781db4313c79b496c64020.webm?t=1764731549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/006142025b781db4313c79b496c64020.mp4?t=1764731549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/45addf1ca3c6fbf39ee6f269077d3044.avif?t=1764731549\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中的敌人将考验你的反应速度与战术智慧！从变异的人类、暴动的机械体，到诡异的生物和黏糊的史莱姆，每种敌人都有独特的攻击方式和行为模式。而它们身上随机装备的义肢，让每次遭遇都充满变数！每一层的BOSS挑战更是极富创意与挑战性，它们不仅攻击力惊人，还拥有独特的战斗机制。仔细观察、适应敌人的行为，利用你的战术突破难关，证明你就是最强战士！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/c2ba94510ae458941504d8bed54b266a.poster.avif?t=1764731549\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/c2ba94510ae458941504d8bed54b266a.webm?t=1764731549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282130/extras/c2ba94510ae458941504d8bed54b266a.mp4?t=1764731549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带上你的战术装备，冲破一切阻碍，迎接挑战，打出最爽的一击吧！</p>",
